          <text>increase</text>
        </annotation>
        <annotation id="T12">
          <infon key="type">Variable</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T12</infon>
          <location length="15" offset="379"/>
          <text>food production</text>
        </annotation>
        <relation id="E3">
          <infon key="type">Increase</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">event</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">E3</infon>
          <node refid="T3" role="Increase"/>
          <node refid="T12" role="Theme"/>
        </relation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">4</infon>
        <offset>456</offset>
        <text>One such problem is the accumulation of nitrate in both freshwater and coastal marine ecosystems.
</text>
        <annotation id="T4">
          <infon key="type">Increase</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T4</infon>
          <location length="12" offset="480"/>
          <text>accumulation</text>
        </annotation>
        <annotation id="T13">
          <infon key="type">Variable</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T13</infon>
          <location length="56" offset="496"/>
          <text>nitrate in both freshwater and coastal marine ecosystems</text>
        </annotation>
        <relation id="E4">
          <infon key="type">Increase</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">event</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">E4</infon>
          <node refid="T4" role="Increase"/>
          <node refid="T13" role="Theme"/>
        </relation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">5</infon>
        <offset>554</offset>
        <text>Here we establish that ecosystem nitrate accrual exhibits consistent and negative nonlinear correlations with organic carbon availability along a hydrologic continuum from soils, through freshwater systems and coastal margins, to the open ocean.
</text>
        <annotation id="T5">
          <infon key="type">Negative_Correlate</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T5</infon>
          <location length="31" offset="627"/>
          <text>negative nonlinear correlations</text>
        </annotation>
        <annotation id="T14">
          <infon key="type">Variable</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T14</infon>
          <location length="25" offset="577"/>
          <text>ecosystem nitrate accrual</text>
        </annotation>
        <annotation id="T15">
          <infon key="type">Variable</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T15</infon>
          <location length="27" offset="664"/>
          <text>organic carbon availability</text>
        </annotation>
        <relation id="E5">
