      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">10</infon>
        <offset>1550</offset>
        <text>At low organic carbon:nitrate ratios, denitrification appears to constrain the extent of nitrate accretion, once organic carbon and nitrate availability approach the 1:1 stoichiometry of this catabolic process.
</text>
        <annotation id="T9">
          <infon key="type">Increase</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <infon key="brat-id">T9</infon>
