      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">11</infon>
        <offset>1761</offset>
        <text>Collectively, these microbial processes express themselves on local to global scales by restricting the threshold ratios underlying nitrate accrual to a constrained stoichiometric window.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">12</infon>
        <offset>1949</offset>
        <text>Our findings indicate that ecological stoichiometry can help explain the fate of nitrate across disparate environments and in the face of human disturbance.
</text>
      </sentence>
